  "text": "From a more methodological perspective, SKA-31's efficacy at producing arteriolar dilation without the need to stimulate G-protein coupled receptors may render it a novel pharmacological tool to investigate pure EDH-type dilations and related electrical mechanisms of dilation such as direct charge transfer through myoendothelial coupling involving Cx40 as reported for rat small mesenteric arteries [CITATION_1] .",
